#: ../src/docs/guides/network/librenms_monitoring_server.md:660
#, no-wrap
msgid "LibreNMS is a powerful monitoring tool with a full set of features in one application. We have only _just_ scratched the surface on the capabilities. We haven't shown you some of the obvious screens. \n"
