#, no-wrap
msgid "For instance, as soon as you add devices, assuming that all of the SNMP properties are set correctly, you'll start to receive bandwidth, memory utilization, and CPU utilization graphs on each device. We haven't shown you the wealth of transports available besides \"Mail\". \n"
